  "name": "Gross Profit Report - Fulfilled",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"gross-profit-report-fulfilled\">Gross Profit Report - Fulfilled</h1>\n<p>Use the Gross Profit Report - Fulfilled to view details of Fulfilled products within the selected period, including Fulfilled COGS, Fulfilled GP % and $.</p>\n<p>When using this report, please bear the following in mind:</p>\n<ul><li>A maximum date range of one month can be applied</li><li>The report displays both the date the invoice was created and fulfilled, however, the filters provided are for the Fulfilment date only.</li></ul><p>To use the Gross Profit Report - Invoiced:</p>\n<ol><li>Navigate to <strong>Reports &gt; Sales Report &gt; Gross Profit Report - Fulfilled</strong></li><li>Select from the Filters as required </li><li><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"584\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 584px; width: 900px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41348PM.05T5g000018qHEiEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Click <strong>Search</strong></li><li>The results will be displayed</li><li>Click the <strong>Save</strong> disk to export the report in a variety of formats</li></ol><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#Top\">Return to Top</a></p>",
